1
00:02:44,120 --> 00:02:44,720
Xiaoxiao,

2
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,079
you're awake.

3
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,450
Are you feeling uncomfortable anywhere?

4
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,320
How do you feel?

5
00:02:50,320 --> 00:02:51,200
Does it hurt?

6
00:02:51,480 --> 00:02:52,280
Are you dizzy?

7
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,940
I know everything.

8
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,260
Look at you,

9
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,660
risking your own life.

10
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,160
Is it worth it?

11
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,040
Are you silly?

12
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:30,040
Please leave first.

13
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:33,000
I want to be alone for a while.

14
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:04,600
Xiaoxiao.

15
00:04:06,040 --> 00:04:07,300
I'll be right outside.

16
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,320
Call me if you need anything,

17
00:04:10,160 --> 00:04:11,560
or just press the bell.

18
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:56,640
Jin Tian,

19
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:59,200
you know Xiaoxiao.

20
00:04:59,520 --> 00:05:00,400
Seeing her like this,

21
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,660
don't push her for now.

22
00:05:07,680 --> 00:05:09,240
Why don't you go back tonight?

23
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,300
I'll stay with her.

24
00:05:14,400 --> 00:05:15,160
But I'm

25
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:16,880
really worried.

26
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,250
Let me stay here too.

27
00:05:19,160 --> 00:05:20,890
It's no use for you to stay here.

28
00:05:21,440 --> 00:05:22,280
Go back for now

29
00:05:22,280 --> 00:05:23,280
and get some rest.

30
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:25,040
Pack some things,

31
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,570
and you can take over later.

32
00:05:31,520 --> 00:05:33,050
I guess that's the only way.

33
00:05:34,200 --> 00:05:35,800
Call me if anything happens.

34
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:37,570
Go ahead.

35
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,440
You should go back and rest too.

36
00:05:49,440 --> 00:05:50,880
You have a live stream tomorrow.

37
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,760
I'll watch her.

38
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:56,960
No need.

39
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,980
I already canceled it.

40
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,080
Yuan.

41
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,240
You're awake.

42
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,980
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere?

43
00:08:36,559 --> 00:08:37,020
Come on.

44
00:08:38,679 --> 00:08:39,940
Have something to eat.

45
00:08:50,400 --> 00:08:51,960
If you don't eat, I'll eat it myself.

46
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,200
I haven't slept a wink all night.

47
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,000
I'm starving.

48
00:09:13,040 --> 00:09:14,040
It smells so good.

49
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:19,000
Can you eat outside?

50
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:22,170
Finally, you spoke.

51
00:09:24,000 --> 00:09:25,460
Are you here to laugh at me?

52
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:28,840
I just want to see

53
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:30,680
how Lin Xiaoxiao became so stupid.

54
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:33,010
So stupid that I don't even recognize you.

55
00:09:34,040 --> 00:09:35,370
Mind your own business.

56
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,080
Ending up like this,

57
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:38,280
I deserve it, okay?

58
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,360
You are all winners in life.

59
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,280
Only me,

60
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:43,560
no career,

61
00:09:43,560 --> 00:09:44,600
no love.

62
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:45,920
I deserve it all, okay?

63
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:04,520
So you chose to die.

64
00:10:05,800 --> 00:10:06,600
Lin Xiaoxiao,

65
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:08,720
you're such a failure, you know?

66
00:10:08,720 --> 00:10:10,160
If you think this is so humiliating

67
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:11,000
that you want to die,

68
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:11,880
let me tell you,

69
00:10:12,560 --> 00:10:14,440
no one will shed a single tear for you.

70
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:17,000
You'll just become a topic for gossip accounts.

71
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:19,440
'Some influencer commits suicide for love.'

72
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:20,520
You won't even have a name,

73
00:10:20,520 --> 00:10:21,720
just the word 'some.'

74
00:10:23,640 --> 00:10:24,970
I think you're a failure

75
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:26,880
not because you ran into this crap,

76
00:10:26,880 --> 00:10:28,280
but because when faced with this,

77
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,840
you actually chose to die.

78
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:31,960
In this life,

79
00:10:31,960 --> 00:10:33,160
who hasn't met a jerk?

80
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:34,680
Just treat it like stepping in dog poop.

81
00:10:34,680 --> 00:10:35,940
Wash it off and move on.

82
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:39,440
Do you still think your life is hard?

83
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,240
Look outside.

84
00:10:40,720 --> 00:10:41,780
Those caregivers,

85
00:10:41,880 --> 00:10:43,440
looking after so many patients every day,

86
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,120
staying awake all night.

87
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,520
Isn't that hard for them?

88
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:46,880
Those terminal cancer patients,

89
00:10:46,880 --> 00:10:47,680
who've been given a death sentence,

90
00:10:47,680 --> 00:10:48,940
isn't it hard for them?

91
00:10:51,880 --> 00:10:53,610
Everyone dies sooner or later.

92
00:10:54,040 --> 00:10:55,700
The difference is why you die.

93
00:10:56,200 --> 00:10:57,840
Dying for a scumbag like Lu Li,

94
00:10:57,840 --> 00:10:58,840
is it worth it?

95
00:11:40,560 --> 00:11:41,760
You're really crazy.

96
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:45,900
You're so aggressive even when comforting people.

97
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,080
You haven't slept all night.

98
00:12:02,320 --> 00:12:03,980
Why don't you go back and rest?

99
00:12:05,040 --> 00:12:05,560
No need.

100
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:08,320
I charge for five minutes

101
00:12:08,400 --> 00:12:09,660
and talk for two hours.

102
00:12:14,240 --> 00:12:16,170
I saw your stand-up comedy online.

103
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:17,600
It was wonderful.

104
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,000
It seems

105
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:20,400
you've already moved on.

106
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,180
Are you disappointed?

107
00:12:26,520 --> 00:12:27,200
Did you think

108
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:28,840
I should just be depressed

109
00:12:28,840 --> 00:12:29,960
and never recover?

110
00:12:30,760 --> 00:12:31,800
For a strong woman like you,

111
00:12:31,800 --> 00:12:33,930
how could you be beaten down so easily?

112
00:12:34,960 --> 00:12:36,120
Look at my career now.

113
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,720
Don't call me a strong woman.

114
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:47,200
I heard Lu Li set you up.

115
00:12:48,680 --> 00:12:50,340
He wants to completely ban you

116
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,100
and make you pay five million.

117
00:12:53,680 --> 00:12:54,160
Yeah.

118
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:56,650
Didn't expect that, right?

119
00:12:57,920 --> 00:12:59,250
What are you going to do?

120
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:00,720
What can I do?

121
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:01,450
Just bear it.

122
00:13:02,200 --> 00:13:03,240
Anyway, I'm a person

123
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:03,840
with thick skin

124
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,900
and a lot of health.

125
00:13:05,160 --> 00:13:06,480
I'm just a

126
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:08,160
thick-skinned rhino.

127
00:13:08,800 --> 00:13:10,660
I can withstand a hail of bullets.

128
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,440
Who are you?

129
00:13:54,920 --> 00:13:55,980
What are you doing?

130
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,800
Let go.

131
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,040
Don't be impulsive.

132
00:13:58,040 --> 00:13:59,160
Let's talk this out.

133
00:13:59,160 --> 00:13:59,820
Who are you?

134
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,570
What did you do to Xiaoxiao?

135
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:03,880
She almost died.

136
00:14:04,080 --> 00:14:06,720
What does it matter to me if she wants to die or not?

137
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:07,450
I'll hit you.

138
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:08,720
Mr. Lu, you go first.

139
00:14:08,720 --> 00:14:10,520
I'll call the police right away.

140
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:12,540
No need to call the police.

141
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:13,200
Don't go.

142
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,400
Don't go.

143
00:14:18,080 --> 00:14:19,000
Don't go, Lu Li.

144
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,160
Don't move.

145
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:21,660
Don't move.

146
00:14:21,720 --> 00:14:22,640
I'll kill you.

147
00:14:22,880 --> 00:14:23,280
Let go.

148
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:24,400
Lu Li.

149
00:14:52,880 --> 00:14:54,200
Aren't you leaving yet?

150
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:56,130
I'll leave as soon as I finish this.

151
00:14:59,120 --> 00:14:59,800
Recently,

152
00:15:00,440 --> 00:15:02,400
is your classmate Jiangzi doing okay?

153
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:02,860
Not bad.

154
00:15:03,520 --> 00:15:04,650
She looks okay to me.

155
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,760
At worst, she can just quit

156
00:15:06,760 --> 00:15:07,820
or change careers.

157
00:15:07,840 --> 00:15:09,700
It's not like I can't support her.

158
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:11,400
What about the five million?

159
00:15:12,040 --> 00:15:13,100
What five million?

160
00:15:13,800 --> 00:15:14,860
Haven't you heard?

161
00:15:15,360 --> 00:15:16,800
Shengshi is going to sue her

162
00:15:16,800 --> 00:15:17,840
for five million.

163
00:16:21,640 --> 00:16:22,370
You're back.

164
00:16:22,920 --> 00:16:24,580
Why are you back so late today?

165
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,400
Well,

166
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:28,010
I was working overtime.

167
00:16:34,400 --> 00:16:35,800
Why are you looking at me?

168
00:16:36,480 --> 00:16:37,040
Nothing.

169
00:16:37,520 --> 00:16:38,780
About your classmate,

170
00:16:39,080 --> 00:16:40,210
how did your chat go?

171
00:16:42,280 --> 00:16:43,740
I finally calmed her down.

172
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,920
If it weren't for that bastard Lu Li,

173
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:47,920
she wouldn't have become like this.

174
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,720
Did you make things clear with Lu Li?

175
00:16:57,240 --> 00:16:57,960
I did.

176
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,520
It's just a ban.

177
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,360
At worst,

178
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:03,490
I'll just go back to my old profession.

179
00:17:04,599 --> 00:17:05,680
I'm so talented.

180
00:17:05,680 --> 00:17:07,940
Why would I be afraid of not finding a job?

181
00:17:10,400 --> 00:17:11,560
I'm so happy.

182
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:14,240
Lying flat at home,

183
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:15,599
eating and drinking.

184
00:17:15,599 --> 00:17:16,930
Nothing to worry about.

185
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,660
I can finally have a good rest.

186
00:17:20,760 --> 00:17:22,359
I think it looks pretty good.

187
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:13,560
Baby.

188
00:18:14,280 --> 00:18:14,760
Get up.

189
00:18:15,880 --> 00:18:16,680
I won't get up.

190
00:18:17,880 --> 00:18:19,440
I don't have to work.

191
00:18:19,840 --> 00:18:20,360
Hurry up.

192
00:18:20,360 --> 00:18:21,960
Get up. I'll take you somewhere.

193
00:18:21,960 --> 00:18:23,720
Where are we going again?

194
00:18:24,960 --> 00:18:26,620
You'll know when we get there.

195
00:18:27,240 --> 00:18:28,000
But...

196
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:29,680
I don't want to get up.

197
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:30,490
No, hurry up.

198
00:18:30,640 --> 00:18:31,120
Get up.

199
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:33,320
I don't want to go.

200
00:18:33,840 --> 00:18:34,760
Hurry up.

201
00:18:35,240 --> 00:18:36,040
I'm telling you.

202
00:18:36,040 --> 00:18:37,560
I have a bit of a fever.

203
00:18:38,200 --> 00:18:38,680
No way.

204
00:18:38,680 --> 00:18:39,720
I can't get up.

205
00:18:40,080 --> 00:18:40,640
A fever?

206
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:42,360
Let me feel it.

207
00:18:45,480 --> 00:18:46,540
You're burning up.

208
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:49,700
Then you need to rest well.

209
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,730
You can't go anywhere else.

210
00:18:51,880 --> 00:18:52,810
Get up right now.

211
00:18:54,680 --> 00:18:55,880
I don't want to get up.

212
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:56,560
Let's go.

213
00:18:56,560 --> 00:18:57,320
Go wash up.

214
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:12,280
Be good,

215
00:19:12,480 --> 00:19:13,210
and eat this.

216
00:19:21,880 --> 00:19:22,680
Auntie.

217
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,240
I'm sorry.

218
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:27,200
I was so foolish

219
00:19:27,200 --> 00:19:28,280
to be used by Lu Li,

220
00:19:29,680 --> 00:19:31,210
which ended up hurting you.

221
00:19:32,200 --> 00:19:33,930
This has nothing to do with you.

222
00:19:34,720 --> 00:19:35,850
Don't overthink it.

223
00:19:39,160 --> 00:19:39,880
Auntie.

224
00:19:50,560 --> 00:19:52,760
The nurse just asked me to go to the front desk.

225
00:19:52,760 --> 00:19:54,020
I'll leave this to you.

226
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,900
The window isn't open.

227
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,400
No fresh air can get in.

228
00:20:13,240 --> 00:20:13,840
Oh, right.

229
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:16,400
The one you left at home,

230
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,290
the lavender diffuser,

231
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,450
I brought it for you.

232
00:20:20,400 --> 00:20:22,160
This hospital smells like disinfectant.

233
00:20:22,160 --> 00:20:23,560
You must not be used to it.

234
00:20:24,080 --> 00:20:25,410
I'll put it here for you.

235
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:27,240
Also,

236
00:20:29,200 --> 00:20:31,120
I brought you a travel mug.

237
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:33,210
Drink from this.

238
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:34,440
It's more convenient.

239
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,560
Jin Tian, why do you care so much?

240
00:20:36,680 --> 00:20:38,720
We have nothing to do with each other anymore.

241
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,080
What do you mean we have nothing to do with each other?

242
00:20:40,080 --> 00:20:40,600
It's fine.

243
00:20:40,600 --> 00:20:42,060
Will the hospital call me?

244
00:20:42,840 --> 00:20:44,770
I'm still your emergency contact.

245
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:50,600
There's no more hot water.

246
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:51,530
I'll go get some.

247
00:21:23,400 --> 00:21:24,040
Watch your step.

248
00:21:24,040 --> 00:21:24,970
Watch your step.

249
00:21:25,680 --> 00:21:26,610
What is this for?

250
00:21:27,320 --> 00:21:28,850
Watch your step carefully.

251
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,220
Buy a warning sign.

252
00:21:32,080 --> 00:21:32,440
Lili.

253
00:21:35,720 --> 00:21:36,780
Let's get married.

254
00:21:40,520 --> 00:21:41,580
This is too sudden.

255
00:21:45,320 --> 00:21:46,120
Your ID and household register,

256
00:21:46,120 --> 00:21:47,380
I brought them for you.

257
00:21:54,920 --> 00:21:56,250
I know it's a bit sudden,

258
00:21:58,840 --> 00:21:59,770
but I'm serious.

259
00:22:09,560 --> 00:22:10,080
This

260
00:22:11,800 --> 00:22:14,330
is something I had someone make out of carbon.

261
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:15,840
Time was short,

262
00:22:15,840 --> 00:22:16,900
so it's a bit rough.

263
00:22:17,400 --> 00:22:18,460
Please don't mind.

264
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:22,340
I know others propose with diamonds,

265
00:22:23,840 --> 00:22:24,900
but let me tell you,

266
00:22:25,840 --> 00:22:27,560
the molecular structure of diamonds

267
00:22:27,560 --> 00:22:28,420
is also carbon.

268
00:22:31,880 --> 00:22:33,640
However, the molecular structure of this ring

269
00:22:33,640 --> 00:22:35,700
is more stable than a diamond ring's.

270
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:38,010
So using it to propose to you

271
00:22:38,840 --> 00:22:39,840
is more suitable.

272
00:22:44,520 --> 00:22:45,720
Didn't we agree

273
00:22:47,560 --> 00:22:49,220
to face everything together?

274
00:22:55,280 --> 00:22:55,360
[Mind the step]

275
00:22:55,360 --> 00:23:00,440
[Mind the step]

276
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:01,520
I can marry you,

277
00:23:01,840 --> 00:23:02,700
[Mind the step]

278
00:23:02,880 --> 00:23:04,840
but I want a prenuptial agreement.

279
00:23:06,320 --> 00:23:08,880
I'm still a big blogger with millions of fans after all.

280
00:23:08,880 --> 00:23:10,320
A starved camel is still bigger than a horse.

281
00:23:10,320 --> 00:23:11,380
I can't take a loss.

282
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:13,560
No way.

283
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:17,400
If you become successful in the future,

284
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,400
wouldn't I be losing out big time?

285
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:19,930
Besides,

286
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:22,530
you know I'm a calculating person,

287
00:23:23,320 --> 00:23:24,980
would I let myself take a loss?

288
00:23:25,600 --> 00:23:27,730
If we're getting married, it's today.

289
00:23:32,080 --> 00:23:32,940
[Mind the step]

290
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:35,820
[Mind the step]

291
00:23:47,960 --> 00:23:50,090
Have you really thought this through?

292
00:23:56,000 --> 00:23:57,800
Marriage is such a sacred thing,

293
00:23:59,320 --> 00:24:01,520
if I had even the slightest hesitation,

294
00:24:01,880 --> 00:24:04,080
I wouldn't have brought you here today.

295
00:24:08,000 --> 00:24:08,960
You once said

296
00:24:10,480 --> 00:24:11,640
us drifting in Beijing

297
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:13,500
is like being comrades-in-arms.

298
00:24:14,160 --> 00:24:15,420
Since we are comrades,

299
00:24:16,960 --> 00:24:19,760
we must live, die, advance, and retreat together.

300
00:24:22,200 --> 00:24:23,660
My greatest wish right now

301
00:24:23,840 --> 00:24:25,970
is that when you're charging forward,

302
00:24:26,200 --> 00:24:28,200
you can safely leave your back to me.

303
00:24:41,320 --> 00:24:41,680
Lili,

304
00:24:43,640 --> 00:24:44,170
marry me,

305
00:24:44,840 --> 00:24:45,360
okay?

306
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,250
Let's go.

307
00:26:14,400 --> 00:26:16,200
For better, for worse,

308
00:26:16,880 --> 00:26:18,440
for richer, for poorer,

309
00:26:18,960 --> 00:26:20,800
in sickness and in health,

310
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,720
in youth and in old age,

311
00:26:23,200 --> 00:26:24,000
We will both

312
00:26:24,240 --> 00:26:25,560
stand together through thick and thin,

313
00:26:25,560 --> 00:26:26,800
share each other's hardships,

314
00:26:26,800 --> 00:26:28,440
and be lifelong companions.

315
00:26:28,840 --> 00:26:29,960
We will surely

316
00:26:29,960 --> 00:26:31,840
uphold the vows we made today.

317
00:26:41,560 --> 00:26:42,080
Look.

318
00:26:42,520 --> 00:26:43,520
What a great shot.

319
00:26:45,320 --> 00:26:45,780
Well...

320
00:26:48,680 --> 00:26:51,810
You can't blame me for acting first and reporting later.

321
00:26:52,360 --> 00:26:54,220
You've done this plenty of times.

322
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,770
First with smoking,

323
00:26:56,040 --> 00:26:57,300
and now with marriage.

324
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,680
Uncle, Aunt,

325
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:01,400
this is indeed a bit sudden.

326
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:02,800
Lili.

327
00:27:02,800 --> 00:27:03,930
What did you call me?

328
00:27:09,480 --> 00:27:10,610
That's more like it.

329
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,320
Look.

330
00:27:11,800 --> 00:27:12,760
Luo Xin has been like this

331
00:27:12,760 --> 00:27:14,080
since he was a child.

332
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,640
He doesn't talk much,

333
00:27:15,640 --> 00:27:17,680
but he always does big things quietly.

334
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:19,240
He really gave us a scare.

335
00:27:19,480 --> 00:27:20,280
Fortunately,

336
00:27:20,280 --> 00:27:21,760
it's a pleasant surprise this time,

337
00:27:21,760 --> 00:27:22,600
not a shock.

338
00:27:25,160 --> 00:27:25,760
By the way,

339
00:27:26,400 --> 00:27:27,460
about the wedding,

340
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:28,770
what are your plans?

341
00:27:30,240 --> 00:27:31,280
We've discussed it.

342
00:27:31,280 --> 00:27:32,160
There's no rush.

343
00:27:32,160 --> 00:27:33,200
We'll hold it

344
00:27:33,200 --> 00:27:34,200
when you recover.

345
00:27:35,120 --> 00:27:35,520
Good.

346
00:27:35,840 --> 00:27:36,900
That's wonderful.

347
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,520
Look at your daughter-in-law.

348
00:27:38,520 --> 00:27:39,720
She's so thoughtful.

349
00:27:40,640 --> 00:27:41,970
You must treat her well.

350
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:47,730
Mom, Dad,

351
00:27:48,080 --> 00:27:49,880
I need to take this call outside.

352
00:27:54,440 --> 00:27:55,200
Mr. Yang.

353
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:56,560
Hello, Jiangzi.

354
00:27:56,560 --> 00:27:57,600
It's been a while.

355
00:27:57,880 --> 00:27:58,800
How have you been lately?

356
00:27:58,800 --> 00:27:59,530
Are you free?

357
00:27:59,840 --> 00:28:00,970
Let's get together.

358
00:28:01,040 --> 00:28:02,200
No problem.

359
00:28:02,760 --> 00:28:03,960
Where should we meet?

360
00:28:08,600 --> 00:28:09,530
Dongfeng: 1905.

361
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:22,650
Why are you here?

362
00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:25,760
Did Yang Shuo invite you?

363
00:28:26,760 --> 00:28:27,960
Did he invite you too?

364
00:28:28,440 --> 00:28:28,760
Yes.

365
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,690
I heard you got married.

366
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,680
We just got our marriage certificate.

367
00:28:47,680 --> 00:28:48,740
Congratulations.

368
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,040
Thank you.

369
00:28:56,600 --> 00:28:58,240
Long time no see, you two.

370
00:28:58,240 --> 00:28:59,400
Mr. Yang.

371
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:00,850
Long time no see.

372
00:29:01,000 --> 00:29:01,920
You look great.

373
00:29:02,480 --> 00:29:03,080
Not bad.

374
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,120
A while ago,

375
00:29:04,120 --> 00:29:05,600
I went to Sanya to relax.

376
00:29:06,120 --> 00:29:06,720
No wonder.

377
00:29:07,280 --> 00:29:07,720
Yeah.

378
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,680
The sunshine there,

379
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,200
the beaches,

380
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:10,130
and the bikinis.

381
00:29:10,960 --> 00:29:12,220
Who could resist that?

382
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:16,660
Happy wedding.

383
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,120
Thank you.

384
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:21,780
I'll gladly accept it.

385
00:29:22,760 --> 00:29:23,640
What do you need us for?

386
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:24,400
Why invite us here?

387
00:29:24,400 --> 00:29:25,460
What is this place?

388
00:29:25,760 --> 00:29:26,760
What do you think?

389
00:29:27,920 --> 00:29:28,780
My new company.

390
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:30,920
New company?

391
00:29:32,320 --> 00:29:33,960
While I was on vacation,

392
00:29:33,960 --> 00:29:35,280
I also secured some financing.

393
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:36,320
I founded an

394
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:38,040
internet media company.

395
00:29:46,120 --> 00:29:47,560
Alpaca Ranch?

396
00:29:48,360 --> 00:29:49,490
Alpacas are so cute.

397
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,450
Let's go.

398
00:29:50,800 --> 00:29:52,000
I'll show you around.

399
00:30:05,120 --> 00:30:07,380
This is a lounge area on the second floor.

400
00:30:07,440 --> 00:30:09,280
We also put a mascot here.

401
00:30:11,280 --> 00:30:13,080
Be careful. It might spit on you.

402
00:30:15,240 --> 00:30:16,800
You're getting more and more scheming.

403
00:30:16,800 --> 00:30:18,400
Keeping such a cute pet in the company,

404
00:30:18,400 --> 00:30:20,060
who would want to get off work?

405
00:30:20,240 --> 00:30:21,680
You know me best.

406
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:24,240
You're so cheesy.

407
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,480
I'm not being cheesy.

408
00:30:29,720 --> 00:30:30,580
This is called,

409
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:32,700
"Brother, don't kill me."

410
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:34,920
Please have a seat, you two.

411
00:30:34,920 --> 00:30:36,400
Come, sit.

412
00:30:36,800 --> 00:30:38,400
What did you call us here for?

413
00:30:41,040 --> 00:30:42,400
While I was away,

414
00:30:42,960 --> 00:30:43,960
I heard

415
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:46,100
you were bullied a lot by Lu Li.

416
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:48,600
You signed an unfair contract with him.

417
00:30:49,240 --> 00:30:50,440
I received a lawyer's letter,

418
00:30:50,440 --> 00:30:52,100
asking me to pay five million.

419
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:54,360
You are just foolish,

420
00:30:54,520 --> 00:30:56,180
signing any kind of contract.

421
00:31:00,880 --> 00:31:01,320
Alright.

422
00:31:01,320 --> 00:31:02,580
Since that's the case,

423
00:31:02,800 --> 00:31:04,800
you two should unite against the outside.

424
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,640
Use my place as your core base

425
00:31:06,960 --> 00:31:08,160
and open fire on Lu Li.

426
00:31:10,920 --> 00:31:11,640
Of course.

427
00:31:14,560 --> 00:31:15,420
What about you?

428
00:31:16,520 --> 00:31:17,000
Sure.

429
00:31:17,920 --> 00:31:19,160
It's time to settle my score

430
00:31:19,160 --> 00:31:20,090
with him anyway.

431
00:31:26,160 --> 00:31:26,840
Maile.

432
00:31:26,960 --> 00:31:27,440
Aiwei.

433
00:31:27,800 --> 00:31:28,730
Why are you here?

434
00:31:29,320 --> 00:31:29,920
I quit.

435
00:31:30,560 --> 00:31:32,000
With the company like this,

436
00:31:32,000 --> 00:31:33,730
there's no point in me staying.

437
00:31:34,080 --> 00:31:34,720
Maile

438
00:31:34,720 --> 00:31:35,760
is our

439
00:31:35,760 --> 00:31:36,400
official

440
00:31:36,760 --> 00:31:37,690
first employee.

441
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,920
Let's get down to business.

442
00:31:39,920 --> 00:31:40,720
Let me show you

443
00:31:41,280 --> 00:31:42,680
Luli's latest contract.

444
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:53,720
It's obviously an unfair contract.

445
00:31:54,280 --> 00:31:55,400
But for those bloggers,

446
00:31:55,400 --> 00:31:56,360
I don't think they have a choice.

447
00:31:56,360 --> 00:31:57,560
They're in a dilemma.

448
00:31:58,400 --> 00:32:00,080
Plus with some of Luli's tactics,

449
00:32:00,080 --> 00:32:01,240
most of them

450
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,530
still compromised.

451
00:32:08,040 --> 00:32:09,970
Luli really hasn't changed at all.

452
00:32:11,640 --> 00:32:12,840
Most bloggers

453
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,980
hope to monetize as soon as possible.

454
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:18,330
That's exactly the mindset he's exploiting.

455
00:32:19,600 --> 00:32:21,130
If we want to take down Luli,

456
00:32:21,880 --> 00:32:23,320
Jiangzi, your power alone

457
00:32:23,320 --> 00:32:24,560
is far from enough.

458
00:32:24,720 --> 00:32:27,240
And it can easily be misunderstood as a personal grudge.

459
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:28,760
All bloggers, big and small,

460
00:32:28,760 --> 00:32:29,490
must stand up

461
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:31,200
to build up momentum.

462
00:32:33,120 --> 00:32:34,360
With those bloggers,

463
00:32:34,680 --> 00:32:36,080
I have some connections.

464
00:32:36,160 --> 00:32:37,960
I can find a way to convince them.

465
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:42,920
Alpaca Ranch,

466
00:32:42,920 --> 00:32:44,400
have you opened an account?

467
00:32:44,400 --> 00:32:45,660
I just applied for one.

468
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,620
Then let's do a live stream

469
00:32:47,760 --> 00:32:49,720
and let all the bloggers speak out.

470
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,400
Sure.

471
00:32:55,640 --> 00:32:56,570
Do you agree too?

472
00:33:13,000 --> 00:33:14,460
You want me to step forward

473
00:33:14,920 --> 00:33:16,120
and accuse Luli?

474
00:33:21,840 --> 00:33:23,360
He'll squeeze me to death.

475
00:33:23,880 --> 00:33:26,610
That's why we need everyone to stand up together.

476
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:30,530
Will that even work?

477
00:33:32,320 --> 00:33:33,180
Just look at me.

478
00:33:33,720 --> 00:33:36,050
I'm a living example right in front of you.

479
00:33:38,000 --> 00:33:39,640
If you go against the company,

480
00:33:39,640 --> 00:33:40,880
you won't just lose your account.

481
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:43,600
You might not even be able to work in this industry anymore.

482
00:33:43,600 --> 00:33:44,240
Unless

483
00:33:44,560 --> 00:33:46,720
you want to bury your head in the sand.

484
00:33:47,040 --> 00:33:48,840
You do whatever the company says

485
00:33:49,440 --> 00:33:50,240
and eat whatever garbage

486
00:33:50,240 --> 00:33:51,320
they feed you.

487
00:33:53,040 --> 00:33:54,040
What happened to me today

488
00:33:54,040 --> 00:33:55,640
will happen to you tomorrow.

489
00:34:00,480 --> 00:34:01,880
I understand all of that.

490
00:34:02,520 --> 00:34:03,120
But...

491
00:34:05,360 --> 00:34:07,000
What if this doesn't work?

492
00:34:08,159 --> 00:34:09,400
I'll have no way out.

493
00:34:14,520 --> 00:34:15,040
Feifei,

494
00:34:16,800 --> 00:34:18,730
I really understand your dilemma.

495
00:34:19,159 --> 00:34:20,560
I don't want to force you.

496
00:34:23,239 --> 00:34:24,370
But you have to know,

497
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,650
even though you're helping me,

498
00:34:26,880 --> 00:34:28,880
you're helping yourself even more.

499
00:34:31,000 --> 00:34:32,679
Do you want to be a blogger

500
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:34,120
who can't even say no?

501
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:45,159
Will I be the only one standing up?

502
00:34:46,239 --> 00:34:48,000
If it's just me,

503
00:34:49,360 --> 00:34:51,480
it won't be of any use.

504
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,639
If you're willing to join,

505
00:34:54,639 --> 00:34:56,370
we'll have thirteen bloggers.

506
00:35:09,200 --> 00:35:10,960
If everyone else is joining,

507
00:35:11,880 --> 00:35:12,640
count me in.

508
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,520
Did Jiangzi contact you?

509
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:33,810
I heard more than a dozen bloggers agreed.

510
00:35:35,040 --> 00:35:36,040
That's good.

511
00:35:36,960 --> 00:35:38,000
I hope this livestream

512
00:35:38,000 --> 00:35:39,800
can draw everyone's attention.

513
00:35:39,880 --> 00:35:40,360
Lu Li,

514
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:41,290
this is goodbye.

515
00:35:41,480 --> 00:35:43,680
Otherwise, I'll have no freedom at all.

516
00:35:43,680 --> 00:35:44,920
My fans keep DMing to scold me

517
00:35:44,920 --> 00:35:46,180
for taking random ads.

518
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:19,000
I heard Yang Shuo

519
00:36:20,040 --> 00:36:21,680
got Ai Wei and Jiang Zi

520
00:36:21,680 --> 00:36:23,040
to start a new company.

521
00:36:24,240 --> 00:36:26,170
It seems they're coming after you.

522
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,040
With just the few of them,

523
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,860
what can they possibly do?

524
00:36:31,520 --> 00:36:32,480
Ai Wei and Jiang Zi

525
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,680
are dead ends.

526
00:36:34,040 --> 00:36:35,000
I don't even know

527
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:35,800
why Yang Shuo

528
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:37,200
is mixing with them.

529
00:36:40,120 --> 00:36:41,380
You should be careful.

530
00:36:41,760 --> 00:36:44,160
They might poach people from your company.

531
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:44,720
Mr. Li,

532
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,920
don't worry about that.

533
00:36:45,920 --> 00:36:47,040
Our company's bloggers

534
00:36:47,040 --> 00:36:48,170
aren't that stupid.

535
00:36:48,600 --> 00:36:49,680
Where the resources are,

536
00:36:49,680 --> 00:36:51,000
that's where they'll be.

537
00:36:51,000 --> 00:36:52,120
Ideals and sentiments

538
00:36:52,120 --> 00:36:54,000
are just for coaxing children.

539
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:01,920
So the core this time...

540
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:02,520
Yang Shuo,

541
00:37:03,200 --> 00:37:04,920
tell him to raise the camera angle a bit.

542
00:37:04,920 --> 00:37:05,480
Okay.

543
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:06,410
It's too low.

544
00:37:06,640 --> 00:37:09,040
But this is just going through the motions.

545
00:37:10,280 --> 00:37:11,210
Zedong, Zedong.

546
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:12,480
It's too dark over there.

547
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:14,240
Your face looks half bright, half dark.

548
00:37:14,240 --> 00:37:15,000
We can adjust it.

549
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,260
Make it a bit brighter.

550
00:37:19,560 --> 00:37:20,560
Is the angle okay?

551
00:37:21,960 --> 00:37:22,480
Say something.

552
00:37:22,480 --> 00:37:23,140
Let me hear.

553
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:25,260
One, two, three. One, two, three.

554
00:37:27,680 --> 00:37:28,680
Don't worry.

555
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:30,120
I'm already on my way.

556
00:37:30,600 --> 00:37:31,600
If there's no traffic,

557
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:32,320
I should

558
00:37:32,320 --> 00:37:33,650
be there in half an hour.

559
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:48,520
Mr. Lu.

560
00:37:50,360 --> 00:37:50,820
Feifei.

561
00:37:51,040 --> 00:37:52,960
Where are you going in such a hurry?

562
00:37:52,960 --> 00:37:54,560
I'm going out to see a friend.

563
00:37:54,800 --> 00:37:56,660
To see a friend at the alpaca farm.

564
00:37:58,560 --> 00:38:00,240
Going at this time

565
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:01,040
is just right.

566
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:06,320
How did you know I was going to the alpaca farm?

567
00:38:06,320 --> 00:38:07,320
Of course I know.

568
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:10,330
You're not really silly enough to go, are you?

569
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:13,280
Do you want to ruin your career

570
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,800
so quickly?

571
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,280
No, Mr. Lu.

572
00:38:21,920 --> 00:38:22,600
We just...

573
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,120
Feifei.

574
00:38:23,960 --> 00:38:25,360
If you had nothing right now

575
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:26,690
and were empty-handed,

576
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:28,650
you could go out of loyalty.

577
00:38:29,520 --> 00:38:32,280
But now you've achieved a certain level of success,

578
00:38:32,280 --> 00:38:35,120
and you have a hundred or two hundred thousand fans, right?

579
00:38:35,120 --> 00:38:35,840
Just this afternoon,

580
00:38:35,840 --> 00:38:37,040
I also told Mr. Li that

581
00:38:37,720 --> 00:38:39,760
the company's future business resources

582
00:38:39,760 --> 00:38:41,290
will lean more towards you.

583
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:47,520
So for every step you take now,

584
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,340
you must think it through.

585
00:39:02,160 --> 00:39:02,520
Look.

586
00:39:04,120 --> 00:39:05,560
Landai is looking for a streamer

587
00:39:05,560 --> 00:39:07,420
for their new season's products.

588
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:08,880
I didn't lie to you, did I?

589
00:40:01,680 --> 00:40:02,480
Stop calling.

590
00:40:04,640 --> 00:40:05,770
They're not coming.

591
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:40,180
How did things turn out like this?

592
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:42,320
Need you ask?

593
00:40:43,200 --> 00:40:44,600
Lu Li must have found out.

594
00:40:46,800 --> 00:40:48,460
How could Lu Li possibly know?

595
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:51,920
Then you should be the one to answer.

596
00:40:52,360 --> 00:40:53,200
Me?

597
00:40:54,040 --> 00:40:54,800
Who else?

598
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:57,400
What do you mean?

599
00:40:58,480 --> 00:40:59,680
For such an important plan,

600
00:40:59,680 --> 00:41:01,480
shouldn't it be more secretive?

601
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,880
I talked to them one by one in private.

602
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,360
How else could I hide it?

603
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:07,160
Then how did the word get out?

604
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,360
How should I know?

605
00:41:11,160 --> 00:41:12,800
You should have drafted

606
00:41:12,800 --> 00:41:14,120
a statement against Lu Li in advance.

607
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:14,880
When talking,

608
00:41:14,880 --> 00:41:17,340
you should have let them sign the statement.

609
00:41:18,480 --> 00:41:19,640
Hindsight is 20/20.

610
00:41:23,200 --> 00:41:25,000
I think since things have come to this,

611
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,730
let's fill our stomachs first.

612
00:41:26,760 --> 00:41:27,200
Okay?

613
00:41:29,840 --> 00:41:32,040
It's not your first day in the business,

614
00:41:32,160 --> 00:41:33,290
yet you're so naive.

615
00:41:33,840 --> 00:41:36,700
No wonder you wouldn't know if someone sold you out.

616
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:38,120
I am naive.

617
00:41:38,280 --> 00:41:41,480
Otherwise, I wouldn't have been sold out by you back then.

618
00:41:42,760 --> 00:41:43,360
Jiangzi.

619
00:41:51,200 --> 00:41:51,880
It's okay.

620
00:41:53,320 --> 00:41:54,760
I know you won't forgive me.

621
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:57,490
Anyway, we don't need to be friends in the future.

622
00:41:57,520 --> 00:41:58,520
After dealing with Lu Li,

623
00:41:58,520 --> 00:42:00,050
we'll go our separate ways.

624
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:02,240
Fine.

625
00:42:23,600 --> 00:42:25,600
Since our goals are aligned,

626
00:42:25,960 --> 00:42:26,320
well,

627
00:42:26,840 --> 00:42:28,370
here's to the next success.

628
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:30,770
Let's drink to it first.

629
00:43:10,880 --> 00:43:12,210
Are you feeling better?

630
00:43:21,640 --> 00:43:23,100
Let me pour you some water.

631
00:43:36,560 --> 00:43:36,890
Here.

632
00:43:41,320 --> 00:43:42,250
I'm not thirsty.

633
00:43:47,040 --> 00:43:48,480
I bought you a lot of food.

634
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:50,360
They are all your favorites.

635
00:43:50,840 --> 00:43:52,640
Vitamins are good for your skin.

636
00:43:53,160 --> 00:43:54,040
My friend brought this fruit

637
00:43:54,040 --> 00:43:55,440
from the south.

638
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:56,360
I'll go wash one.

639
00:43:56,360 --> 00:43:58,040
Can you stop nagging

640
00:43:58,040 --> 00:43:59,370
and talking endlessly?

641
00:44:02,800 --> 00:44:04,130
I'll stop talking then.

642
00:44:22,560 --> 00:44:24,720
You keep pacing in front of me.

643
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:26,560
It's making me dizzy.

644
00:44:55,040 --> 00:44:57,320
Jin Tian, why are you still so immature?

645
00:44:57,680 --> 00:44:59,760
Don't you understand what I'm saying?

646
00:44:59,760 --> 00:45:00,720
I told you to get out

647
00:45:00,720 --> 00:45:02,780
and disappear from my sight forever.

648
00:45:06,800 --> 00:45:07,280
Well,

649
00:45:09,080 --> 00:45:10,480
I'll wait in the hallway.

650
00:45:11,440 --> 00:45:13,040
Call me if you need anything.

651
00:45:22,600 --> 00:45:23,160
Jin Tian,

652
00:45:33,240 --> 00:45:33,840
come here.

653
00:45:41,160 --> 00:45:41,760
What is it?

654
00:45:47,520 --> 00:45:49,120
I have something to tell you.

655
00:45:49,320 --> 00:45:50,160
Have a seat.

656
00:46:12,000 --> 00:46:12,720
I'm sorry.

657
00:46:20,960 --> 00:46:21,760
I really am.

658
00:46:23,720 --> 00:46:25,920
I shouldn't have treated you like that.

659
00:46:26,440 --> 00:46:27,560
You know what?

660
00:46:28,880 --> 00:46:30,680
The better you treat me,

661
00:46:31,320 --> 00:46:33,080
the more I dislike myself,

662
00:46:33,080 --> 00:46:35,080
and the more I hate myself.

663
00:46:35,480 --> 00:46:36,400
Don't say that.

664
00:46:38,040 --> 00:46:39,300
As long as we are alive,

665
00:46:39,640 --> 00:46:41,170
who doesn't make mistakes?

666
00:46:41,520 --> 00:46:42,650
I make mistakes too.

667
00:46:45,840 --> 00:46:47,800
I didn't spend enough time with you,

668
00:46:47,800 --> 00:46:49,400
I didn't care for you enough,

669
00:46:49,480 --> 00:46:51,200
and I didn't support your dreams enough.

670
00:46:51,200 --> 00:46:52,730
Aren't those all my faults?

671
00:46:55,480 --> 00:46:56,080
Actually,

672
00:46:59,680 --> 00:47:01,400
I think we can start over.

673
00:47:05,720 --> 00:47:06,760
Let's pretend

674
00:47:07,280 --> 00:47:08,400
today is

675
00:47:08,520 --> 00:47:09,650
the first day we met.

676
00:47:13,440 --> 00:47:13,920
Hello.

677
00:47:15,480 --> 00:47:16,540
My name is Jin Tian.

678
00:47:18,480 --> 00:47:19,920
Nice to meet you today.

679
00:47:43,880 --> 00:47:45,960
Life doesn't start over.

680
00:47:48,360 --> 00:47:50,080
And we can't go back either.

681
00:47:50,400 --> 00:47:51,640
We don't need to go back.

682
00:47:51,640 --> 00:47:53,320
What we need is to start over.

683
00:47:53,680 --> 00:47:54,600
No.

684
00:47:55,080 --> 00:47:56,680
Even if I had a choice,

685
00:47:56,680 --> 00:47:59,040
I wouldn't choose to start over.

686
00:47:59,080 --> 00:48:00,160
You know what?

687
00:48:01,960 --> 00:48:03,960
I choose to accept who I am now.

688
00:48:04,720 --> 00:48:06,180
Because of what happened,

689
00:48:07,640 --> 00:48:09,680
I became the Lin Xiaoxiao I am today.

690
00:48:10,880 --> 00:48:11,720
Whatever you become,

691
00:48:11,720 --> 00:48:12,640
I accept it.

692
00:48:13,320 --> 00:48:14,640
If you need me to change,

693
00:48:14,640 --> 00:48:16,120
if you like mature men,

694
00:48:16,120 --> 00:48:17,560
I can become a mature man too.

695
00:48:17,560 --> 00:48:18,960
No, it's not that, Jin Tian.

696
00:48:18,960 --> 00:48:20,040
It's not your fault,

697
00:48:20,040 --> 00:48:21,640
and you don't need to change.

698
00:48:21,880 --> 00:48:22,800
It's just that the two of us

699
00:48:22,800 --> 00:48:24,720
can't go back to being in a relationship.

700
00:48:24,720 --> 00:48:25,520
You know?

701
00:48:25,520 --> 00:48:26,800
It's because this marriage

702
00:48:26,800 --> 00:48:28,800
is suffocating me so much

703
00:48:28,800 --> 00:48:30,960
that I don't know what to do.

704
00:48:50,600 --> 00:48:51,200
I'm sorry.

705
00:48:53,320 --> 00:48:54,200
I really am.

706
00:49:04,560 --> 00:49:05,200
Jin Tian.

707
00:49:07,520 --> 00:49:08,280
Thank you.

708
00:49:09,240 --> 00:49:10,500
For the past ten years,

709
00:49:12,120 --> 00:49:13,380
for being so good to me.

710
00:49:16,360 --> 00:49:17,160
How good you've been to me,

711
00:49:17,160 --> 00:49:18,480
I'll always remember.

712
00:49:33,360 --> 00:49:36,560
Now I have a very selfish thought.

713
00:49:37,920 --> 00:49:39,480
If possible,

714
00:49:46,240 --> 00:49:48,640
could we become best friends?

715
00:49:57,840 --> 00:49:59,170
My name is Lin Xiaoxiao.

716
00:50:01,240 --> 00:50:03,000
Can I be your best friend?

717
00:50:20,240 --> 00:50:21,080
Can I?

718
00:50:27,840 --> 00:50:28,900
What are you doing?

719
00:50:32,360 --> 00:50:33,440
What are you doing?

720
00:50:47,480 --> 00:50:48,540
What are you doing?

721
00:51:25,000 --> 00:51:26,060
My name is Jin Tian.

722
00:51:27,640 --> 00:51:28,570
Nice to meet you.

723
00:51:31,200 --> 00:51:32,240
From now on.

724
00:51:33,400 --> 00:51:35,280
I'm your best friend.

725
00:52:10,480 --> 00:52:10,640
I see.
